HEADWORD: Grizzled
<hw>Griz"zled</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Gray; grayish;
sprinkled or mixed with gray; of a mixed white and black.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Grizzled</qex> hair flowing in elf locks.</q> <rj><qau>Sir W.
